RUNTIME DEPENDENCIES (absolutely required)

	sysvinit
	dash (in /bin; you can change all scripts to bash if you want to)
	coreutils
	util-linux
	grep
	filesystem
	glibc


RUNTIME DEPENDENCIES (highly recommended)

	kbd


RUNTIME DEPENDENCIES (recommended)

	kmod
	devd (you have to select providing package)


BUILD DEPENDENCIES

	make
	gcc
	glibc


INSTALL DEPENDENCIES

	make
	coreutils

